    "text": "Expanding Contracting Opportunities for Small Businesses Act of 2021\n\nThis bill increases the allowable award price for federal government contracts with certain small businesses, including socially and economically disadvantaged small businesses, small businesses owned and controlled by women, and small businesses owned and controlled by service-disabled veterans."
